| W0_TEST0 | W0_TEST1 | W0_TEST2 | W0_TEST3 | W0_TEST4 |
+----------+----------+----------+----------+----------+
|        0 | 1.0E+000 | 0A       |          |        0 |
|        3 | 4.0E+000 | 0B       |   C      | 8.1E+001 |
